BOARD AND DEVICES
  the board has 256 plugs for devices
  a device has a memory, a void* object, callbacks for irq, cc, dc
  a memory has a pointer and a size
  a cpu has an instruction pointer and an instruction table
  most void* ref'd in devices will have reverse references too
  the device object will maintain a reference to the board

EXAMPLE DEVICES
  debug
    streamer
  proc
    regproc
    pyproc
    guileproc
    luaproc
    forthproc
  mem
    ram
    disk